text: The 2010–11 Cosmopolitan Soccer League was the 87th season of the league's existence, as well as the sixteenth season of the league representing parts of the fifth through seventh tiers of the American Soccer Pyramid. The defending champions are the Pancyprian-Freedoms for the First Division East.
